ai-patthana23.35:0.2_0: under the influence of the Dhamma: the Protector of the Three Worlds
ai-patthana23.35:0.3_0: and so on although they arise, they are wholesome.
ai-patthana23.35:1.1_0: ‘This isn’t unskillful, nor is a condition for the support of the skillful.
ai-patthana23.35:1.1_1: Seven on the objects of the six kinds of support,
ai-patthana23.35:2.1_0: Nor do they haven’t arisen in the Dhamma, nor is what is unskillful.
ai-patthana23.35:2.1_1: Six supports six objects of a six objects, six classes of objects,
ai-patthana23.35:3.1_0: You shouldn’t have a good principle not come to be in conformity with the three Dhamma. ...
ai-patthana23.35:4.1_0: Nor do they have arisen in the way beginning, middle, or end. It is a condition for the object of the teaching.
ai-patthana23.35:4.1_1: This is the section in brief.
ai-patthana23.35:5.1_0: ... the seventh objects of repetition have been reborn in the realm of Yet ...
ai-patthana23.35:5.1_1: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
